    <div class="important-box">
      <div class="important-title">Declaration</div>
      <p>By signing this agreement, all parties confirm that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>They have read and understood this agreement</li>
        <li>They agree to be bound by its terms</li>
        <li>All information provided is true and accurate</li>
        <li>They have received a copy of this agreement</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-blocks">
